"|**Any Genre 2** |`anygenre2.jamulus.io:22224`|\n"
"|**Any Genre 3** |`anygenre3.jamulus.io:22624`|\n"
"|**Genre Rock** |`rock.jamulus.io:22424`|\n"
"|**Genre Jazz** |`jazz.jamulus.io:22324`|\n"
"|**Genre Classical/Folk** |`classical.jamulus.io:22524`|\n"
